# Skill #8 - Using Bootstrap

Skill Demonstration Challenge

---

## Instructions

### Objective

Demonstrate how to use Bootstrap to quickly style your web pages.


### Steps

* Copy the template from 
[Demo #20  - Using Bootstrap](https://unco-bacs.org/bacs200/demo/20/bootstrap.html)
* Build your own page template "bacs200/bootstrap.html"
* Customize this page template with some boilerplate code for new pages
* Copy the template from 
[Demo #21  - Tab Views](https://unco-bacs.org/bacs200/demo/21/index.html)
* Build your own page template "bacs200/tabs.html"
* Customize this page template with some boilerplate code for new pages
* Login to the Sensei Homework Dashboard and view your work in the Skills section


### Requirements

* Screen shot "bacs200/skills/bootstrap.png"


